OL,3,CCalls in Parliament for judge-led
OL,4,Cinquiry into who bombed Birmingham
OL,6,FThere were repeated calls in
OL,7,FParliament today for a judge-led
OL,8,Finquiry in the Birmingham Pub Bombings
OL,9,F- rather than the Government's
OL,10,Fproposal to widen the remit of a
OL,11,Fcommission set up to look into deaths
OL,12,Fconnected with the Troubles in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,15,FAt the end of October the Home Office
OL,16,Fsaid there would be no public inquiry
OL,17,Finto the attacks, which killed 21
OL,18,Fpeople and injured more than 220 when
OL,19,Fbombs exploded in two pubs, the
OL,20,FMulberry Bush and Tavern in the Town,
OL,21,Fon 21 November 1974.
