OL,3,CCalls in Parliament for judge-led
OL,4,Cinquiry into who bombed Birmingham
OL,6,FThe Home Office said the Independent
OL,7,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,8,FInformation Recovery, which is already
OL,9,Finvestigating cases linked to The
OL,10,FTroubles, would look into the Pub
OL,11,FBombings.
OL,13,FThe Birmingham Hodge Hill and Solihull
OL,14,FNorth MP, Liam Byrne, argued it would
OL,15,Fnot deliver the truth, and that the
OL,16,Ffamilies did not have faith in the
OL,17,Fprocess.
