OL,3,CCalls in Parliament for judge-led
OL,4,Cinquiry into who bombed Birmingham
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister reiterated his
OL,7,Fbelief the commission is the best way
OL,8,Fforward, but promised a meeting with
OL,9,Fthe victims' families.
OL,11,FFamilies have long campaigned for a
OL,12,Fpublic inquiry into the bombings to
OL,13,Ffind out what the government knew at
OL,14,Fthe time and why no one has been
OL,15,Fsuccessfully brought to justice.
