OL,3,CCalls in Parliament for judge-led
OL,4,Cinquiry into who bombed Birmingham
OL,6,FJulie Hambleton, whose sister Maxine
OL,7,Fdied in the attacks, said that if the
OL,8,Finvestigations go ahead in the
OL,9,Fproposed form, they won't take part,
OL,10,Fdescribing the commission as "obscene"
OL,11,Fas it won't compel witnesses to give
OL,12,Fevidence.
OL,14,FWhat is the Independent Commission for
OL,15,FReconciliation and Information
OL,16,FRecovery?
