OL,3,CCalls in Parliament for judge-led
OL,4,Cinquiry into who bombed Birmingham
OL,6,FThe government said the commission is
OL,7,Fthe primary route for legacy
OL,8,Finvestigations, and that it has
OL,9,Fconfidence in its ability to deliver
OL,10,Finvestigations and accountability. It
OL,11,Fhas powers to conduct criminal
OL,12,Finvestigations into Troubles-related
OL,13,Fevents.
OL,15,FIt is now running over 100
OL,16,Finvestigations, including into the
OL,17,FGuildford pub bombings, the Kingsmill
OL,18,Fmassacre, Warrenpoint and the M62
OL,19,Fcoach bombing.
