OL,6,FThe government has also introduced the
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland Troubles Bill to
OL,8,Freform the commission. It said it
OL,9,Fwould ensure the commission is fully
OL,10,Fhuman-rights complaint and is trusted
OL,11,Fby any victims.
